RACE.RACE_TEXT: FAIR MEADOWS RACE 1 4F Dirt CR: 66. Claiming Purse 4950. FOR THREE YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE SINCE DECEMBER 7, 2022. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 124 lbs. Claiming Price $5,000.

BURTNJOE stalked the front runner through the turn, rated close up at the head of the stretch, and finished well clear of the rest but was unable to catch the winner. EURONTHEMONEY settled in between rivals, trekked two wide around the turn, and prevailed in the stretch duel for the show. TIZ STRONG lacked a needed rally after settling into the second flight and losing ground to rivals with a three wide journey. OVER EZ settled into the second flight, rated as the widest of four abreast around the turn and lost ground to rivals by doing so.
